{"tid":2359561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警拘民主派過程曝光  暴力 橫蠻 無恥","createTime":"2021-01-09T04:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T05:19:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1359f03c71f8220d814270171dea2a62e0276e","tid":2359561,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210109/WRJIFQMDDBCINF6BL5JXV2P4X4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210109%2FWRJIFQMDDBCINF6BL5JXV2P4X4%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=ca1f30ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210109%2FWRJIFQMDDBCINF6BL5JXV2P4X4%2F&h=0cca3749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210109/WRJIFQMDDBCINF6BL5JXV2P4X4/</a><br />\n<br />\n警拘民主派過程曝光 <br />\n暴力 橫蠻 無恥<br />\n<br />\n【歹毒大搜捕】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：民主黨：警圖侵電郵「攞料」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方國安處動用港版國安法中的「顛覆政權罪」，至今拘捕55名民主派人士，拘捕過程高壓、恫嚇、野蠻、無禮，除了以爆門、反手扣壓、伸縮警棍、大鐵鎚「招呼」民主派，並以阻差辦公罪名阻止拍攝搜證過程，警方更即場沒收數以萬計的現金和超市禮券、有關反修例運動的文宣及所有電子產品。警方更要求被捕人的助理為警方「擔凳」。民主派獲保釋後，更發現電子賬戶統統被「政府機構」試圖入侵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9iogIcEdVG-hcBiVqKABo5HyovA=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R6ODWBFRXFHWHIHL7TRT7CXO7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9iogIcEdVG-hcBiVqKABo5HyovA%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR6ODWBFRXFHWHIHL7TRT7CXO7M.jpg&h=f1be8867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■趙家賢居所的門被警方強行破開。 趙家賢提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爆門持棍扣壓 喝「唔好反抗」<br />\n<br />\n協調初選的民主動力召集人趙家賢指，警方抵達他的居所後，懷疑警員在門外等候得不耐煩，強行使用工具破門入屋，他更被警方反手壓倒在沙發上，並遭呼喝：「唔好諗住反抗。」有警員更拿出伸縮警棍在旁監視，並大肆搜查趙家賢居所。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：譚文豪：不容投票 港剩返乜？<br />\n<br />\n民主黨林卓廷亦表示，被捕當日警員持大鐵鎚、鐵筆上門仔細搜屋，阻止其家人拍攝搜證過程。林被捕後遭禁止聯絡家人和同事，其辦事處職員更發現電郵曾遭「國家級黑客」攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_HS4xjdL-PH1GtDmajKkhmRAp9I=/1575x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VKYKYQNNSFBULOHCBXA5JEOMDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_HS4xjdL-PH1GtDmajKkhmRAp9I%3D%2F1575x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVKYKYQNNSFBULOHCBXA5JEOMDA.jpg&h=70694541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙家賢（右）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟至女友家 擸萬現金 禮券<br />\n<br />\n本土派人士劉頴匡透露，他當日是清晨在其女友家中被拘捕，反映警員在進行拘捕前早已跟蹤他。警方搜證時，除取走劉的三部電腦及兩部手機外，更沒收其女友的私人財產，如數萬元現金及超市禮券。劉直斥警方無理，「我都講咗啲錢唔係我」。<br />\n<br />\n劉頴匡表示，被扣押時，警員除了查問其銀行戶口在初選期間的款項往來詳情外，亦多次播放初選召集人戴耀廷及區諾軒談及「35+」的受訪片段。劉稱，警員向他展示的截圖文字為簡體字，質疑有關截圖非由香港警方處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/em03cO2WfEh1n1WVFMcGQQkjo7M=/1025x1654/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E2M22I3IWBCRTL6AINLDED3DYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fem03cO2WfEh1n1WVFMcGQQkjo7M%3D%2F1025x1654%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE2M22I3IWBCRTL6AINLDED3DYY.jpg&h=bcdca167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉頴匡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫助理擔凳 嘲要唔該阿Sir<br />\n<br />\n公民黨李予信指，警方在搜查其住所及辦事處期間，刻意搜查提及「光復香港 時代革命」的文宣，亦撿走與選舉及社會運動有關的文件作調查。李予信更表示，警方曾無理要求其助理為他們「擔凳」，李質疑警方此舉旨在要向他展示「下馬威」。<br />\n<br />\n參加民主派初選被捕馮達浚指，警員搜查時沒收了藝人杜汶澤表演《香港企硬》的紀念T-shirt，又指扣留時不時聽到有警員對被捕民主派冷嘲熱諷，「會話我哋出去聲大大鬧佢哋，入到嚟警署就唔該阿Sir」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aTcYGj1LVosLFzXw0J0AU6B-5t8=/1860x2480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HTG6NYEJ6RECJEHFB2GJNEAY2E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaTcYGj1LVosLFzXw0J0AU6B-5t8%3D%2F1860x2480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHTG6NYEJ6RECJEHFB2GJNEAY2E.jpg&h=90715bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李予信<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搜母姊衣櫃 病房高聲喝斥<br />\n<br />\n曾參加新東初選的鄒家成表示，警方在其家中搜證期間，曾將其母親及姊姊的衣櫃打開、查閱部份書本及文件，共撿走三部電話、電子產品、提款卡、信用卡及護照。鄒表示警方要求他解釋初選時期的每一項銀行紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n灣仔區議會主席楊雪盈指，警員當日曾打算爆門入內，在場議員助理要求拍攝搜證過程時，但警方警告行為阻差辦公。被捕後一度身體不適入院的她稱，有國安處警員疑因不知道其旅遊證件已一早交給其他警員，因而在病房內大聲喝斥她不合作，打擾同房病人，至律師到場方有所收斂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ep0e7av__T67KOtTdZzGN6dTtEo=/879x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PSRU2TBABJBTTAPHWUZKUC5KT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fep0e7av__T67KOtTdZzGN6dTtEo%3D%2F879x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPSRU2TBABJBTTAPHWUZKUC5KT4.jpg&h=75a759e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄒家成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dT-MjU0asd_Z6gz6iZbXSiyD7Zc=/735x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DYIDPS2FKVG3TE2UXFIM7IVZRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdT-MjU0asd_Z6gz6iZbXSiyD7Zc%3D%2F735x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDYIDPS2FKVG3TE2UXFIM7IVZRM.jpg&h=0a690e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊雪盈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阻職員接保釋 濫發限聚告票<br />\n<br />\n民主黨前立法會議員尹兆堅獲釋後，在場守候的民主黨職員、尹的助理及葵青區議員梁國華三人當時互相相隔至少1.5米，卻竟被警方無理指涉違反限聚令，向三人發出告票。<br />\n<br />\n參加衞生服務界初選的劉凱文指，他本在酒店居住自我隔離，他被警方押返住所後， 10多本新舊銀行存摺、一萬多元現金、信用卡及電子產品一律被警方沒收。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NqXqoofzPQ0QpVZxzrJdt3qAsM8=/974x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KPK32RH3KNG5PAD7FMGTMHCJFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNqXqoofzPQ0QpVZxzrJdt3qAsM8%3D%2F974x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKPK32RH3KNG5PAD7FMGTMHCJFE.jpg&h=1fea67c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方連番以限聚令警告尹兆堅助理。尹兆堅fb片段<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要求戴頭套 入侵TG及手機<br />\n<br />\n人民力量陳志全在個人社交網站透露，警方在搜查中從書架逐本書拿出來檢閱。警員最後取走一本初選日誌的筆記本、一份人民力量5月有關內部如何產生候選人的會議紀錄、一份「快必」譚得志被指涉嫌違反港版國安法後由律政司提供的口號統計表。陳更被警方要求扣上手扣及戴頭套。<br />\n<br />\n陳志全獲釋後，指自己的社交程式曾被入侵：「（我）已經好耐冇用Telegram，被警察沒收電話後，今日（昨日）中午一開番SIM卡就不停收到Confirm Code，係乜玩法？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uwndjR8Cz9aS-DxdCVlfPpq-oMk=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PJZUA46TZNFQLOGDP7Z5VT62JM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuwndjR8Cz9aS-DxdCVlfPpq-oMk%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPJZUA46TZNFQLOGDP7Z5VT62JM.jpg&h=de190471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳志全"},{"pid":"863d1b31506e465a7453d7fa9470d45a1b81ad51","tid":2359561,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T04:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43e1a89c24246f8a97b8543789ad45ed9c90aea","tid":2359561,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T04:16:58.000Z","msg":"成班黑社會爛仔"},{"pid":"fe12ec9999bf1109cf9b75f23efb8c445f30b1b9","tid":2359561,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T04:19:43.000Z","msg":"根本黑社會手法"},{"pid":"f3f74af89041c5695d7c4fd4ceccc08f280b9cf7","tid":2359561,"uid":209644,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"沒有無緣無故的愛與恨 要為自己做過的事負責 所以不用再問 &ldquo;係咪真係好憎警察&rdquo; 死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a67e649a5c3512c1728ba73c8d3191d146c7c80","tid":2359561,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T05:19:16.000Z","msg":"照揚公安個套做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}